.IP \(bu 2
Retrieve more records with repeated calls to \fBmongoc_cursor_next()\fP\&.
.IP \(bu 2
Clone a query to repeat execution at a later point with \fBmongoc_cursor_clone()\fP\&.
.IP \(bu 2
Test for errors with \fBmongoc_cursor_error()\fP\&.
